author: rhuijben
msg: Perform a global baton variable rename in the diff editor. Rename all
local variables pointing to an editor_baton to eb, to a directory_baton
db, and fb for file_batons. This matches the style of the other editors
in libsvn_wc.
Use the local eb variable, where the edit_baton was alread locally
cached and update whitespace to match the current conventions.
No functional changes at all.
(I left a few incorrectly spaced svn_wc__adm_abspath() calls that will
be updated to baton references in the next patch)
* subversion/libsvn_wc/diff.c
(dir_baton): Rename dir_baton variable to parent_baton and
edit_baton to eb.
(file_baton): Rename edit_baton variable to eb.
(*): Update callers.
